dct_title_s: Mapa de Rno. de Leon y del Principado de Asturias con las nuevas divisiones
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. In upper margin: Plancha 2a. Atlas nacional de España. Date of publication suggested by mapseller's label on verso. The firm of Andriveau-Goujon was locased at rue du Bac 4 in 1876. cf. Tooley's dictionary of mapmakers.
dct_publisher_sm: Paris ; New-York : Casa de L. Turgis & fils, Rue des Ecoles, 60, [1876?]
